data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!  A portion of the sellers loan is assumable at 3.8% interest.  Check out this one of a kind spacious, freshly updated home with almost 6,000 sq ft. Located in desirable Crockett Ridge Subdivision near Country Club West.  Enjoy beautiful  year round mountain views from the front porch! Main level features open kitchen with island and breakfast nook, pantry, large master suite, family room with fireplace, formal dining room, den/office and much more.  Spacious 14' x 18' screened porch and patio await your grilling and entertainment. Upper level has four bedrooms with walk in closets, bathrooms and  large open room along with a staircase on each end.The lower level has a separate entrance making a great mother-in-law apartment with a kitchen complete with appliances, large living area, bedroom and bathroom along with separate 20' x 20' workshop / storage area.  Call today to schedule your private tour. Recently replaced 70 gallon water heater. Private fenced in back yard for your four legged friends.  Gutter guards installed.  Abundant wildlife nearby.  Seller is providing 1 year home warranty. Call today for your private tour.   If you are needing a lender,  we partner with several that would be happy to assist you.
